#

Strawberry Waffles

25 min
$12
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchEasySweet

Description

Delightfully fluffy waffles topped with fresh strawberries and a drizzle of maple syrup, perfect for breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 2 cups
  • milk: 1 3/4 cups
  • eggs: 2
  • baking powder: 2 tablespoons
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • butter: 1/2 cup
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
  • fresh strawberries: 2 cups, sliced
  • maple syrup: to taste
